					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Be sure to mess with $2006 and $2007 <strong>only</strong> during vblank. So do it as the very first thing in your NMI routine. And after you're done with them, be sure to set the scroll correctly by writing the proper values to $2000 and $2005 before vblank ends. Do anything differently than that and you get the effect you described.</div>

